{"tid":1186723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜確認參選總統，台灣要發大財","createTime":"2019-06-05T06:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T13:21:06.000Z","uid":155095,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90114b1dd05066ab0b95062894c38c41936069a2","tid":1186723,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"台灣國民黨將於下周一（10日）公佈總統初選參選人名單，國民黨副主席曾永權、郝龍斌和組織發展委員會主委李哲華等5人小組，今日特地南下與高雄市長韓國瑜見面，不過行程一改再改、與會時、地也保密。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HDi6jGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHDi6jGy.jpg&h=26fdf5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n郝龍斌今早在高雄中廣電台專訪韓國瑜，面對媒體追問5人小組相關細節，郝龍斌說：「百分之百配合候選人的時間跟地點，他們要求公開或者是私下見面，我們也尊重！」韓國瑜則在近中午時表示，下午會跟5人小組會面，希望能夠私下會談。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ankxCq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FankxCq3.jpg&h=f2d5bc80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙方中午午餐時間在蓮潭會館會談，會後韓證實同意加入國民黨初選「Yes, I do」，後續將遵照黨版初選特別辦法，國政說明會也「一定會參加」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sV2NEo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsV2NEo9.jpg&h=b1a26ead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63c5129f3171ba93b5bd21c4d9a8308e7fc03f57","tid":1186723,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pyp_xXYPj8A/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fpyp_xXYPj8A%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=1b9986b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20190322/20190322000187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20190322%2F20190322000187.jpg&h=6db92db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1553244323-5ddc9c7e1b5f0d5c9bbfaf60ae0f84a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn